A22. Notable auto club ~ AAA
A23. What you might be as busy as ~ ABEE
A25. Royal Air Force officers ~ WINGCOMMANDERS
A32. Jousters will stick it to you ~ LANCE
A33. Bread from the oven ~ TOAST
A34. Zodiac lion ~ LEO
A35. Entr'___ (theater break) ~ ACTE
