A45. A billion years ~ EON
A46. "My Cousin Vinny" star ~ TOMEI
A49. Starbucks order ~ ESPRESSO
A54. He had a hunch about the lab ~ IGOR
A55. They're often innocent ~ BYSTANDERS
A57. Airline with extremely tight security ~ ELAL
